    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[What is the best treatment to decrease pro-inflammatory cytokine release in acute skeletal muscle injury induced by trauma in rats: low-level laser therapy, diclofenac, or cryotherapy?]]></Value>
    </articleTitle>
